BEGIN:VEVENT
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20200922T135621Z
DESCRIPTION:Dear all\,\n \nVote to bring your voice within the Board of Dir
	ectors (Sept 28th-Oct 8th)\nIt only takes 2 minutes to vote ! One share = 
	one vote (the nb of votes is calculated according to the number of shares)
	 \nPlease fond our programme\, videos from our sponsors and all other info
	rmation on our website (English and French version) : https://lepagnol.git
	hub.io/\n \nOur strenghts ?\n*	We are independent (not linked to trade uni
	on organizations)\n*	We represent employee shareholders as a whole. We are
	 regularly in contact with all those who build tomorrow’s bank: (1) acto
	rs on the field who face clients every day and (2) collaborators in centra
	l services\n*	We are close to decision-making center and ambassadors of al
	l areas and jobs at the same time\n \nTo vote:\nYou need your access codes
	 for Esalia and Sharinbox\nESALIA (8 or 9 digit login): https://www.esalia
	.com/\nSharinbox (8 digit login): https://sharinbox.societegenerale.com/\n
	If you can’t find your ID\, launch: https://socgen-portal.globalrelay.co
	m/ <https://socgen-portal.globalrelay.com/> \nIn the search bar : mailer@i
	ssuer.sgss.societegenerale.com <mailto:mailer@issuer.sgss.societegenerale.
	com> \n \nVOTE for LEPAGNOL/LE VAILLANT\, of course!\n \nThank you for you
	r support!\n \nJérôme et Caroline\nLet’s write the future?\n \n
DTEND;TZID="Romance Standard Time":20200928T100000
