	 lang=FR link="#0563C1" vlink="#954F72" style='tab-interval:35.4pt'><div c
	lass=WordSection1><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-lang
	uage:EN-US'>Dear all\,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=
	EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p></span></p><p clas
	s=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>Vote to bring
	 your voice within the Board of Directors (Sept 28<sup>th</sup>-Oct 8<sup>
	th</sup>)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><b><span lang=EN-US styl
	e='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>It only takes 2 minutes to vote</span></b><spa
	n lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'> ! One share = one vote (the 
	<span class=SpellE>nb</span> of votes is calculated according to the numbe
	r of shares) <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US sty
	le='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>Please fond our <span class=SpellE>programme<
	/span>\, videos from our sponsors and all other information on our website
	 (English and French version) : <a href="https://lepagnol.github.io/">http
	s://lepagnol.github.io/</a><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><sp
	an lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p></span></p
	><p class=MsoPlainText><b><span style='color:red'>Our <span class=SpellE>s
	trenghts</span>&nbsp\;?<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><ul style='margin-top:0cm
	' type=disc><li class=xxxmsolistparagraph style='mso-list:l1 level1 lfo7'>
	<span class=xapple-converted-space><span lang=EN-US style='mso-fareast-fon
	t-family:"Times New Roman"\;color:black\;mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>We are<b
	> independent</b></span></span><span lang=EN-US style='mso-fareast-font-fa
	mily:"Times New Roman"\;color:black\;mso-ansi-language:EN-US'> (not linked
	 to trade union organizations)</span><span lang=EN-US style='mso-fareast-f
	ont-family:"Times New Roman"\;mso-ansi-language:EN-US'><o:p></o:p></span><
	/li><li class=xxxmsolistparagraph style='mso-list:l1 level1 lfo7'><span cl
	ass=xapple-converted-space><span lang=EN-US style='mso-fareast-font-family
	:"Times New Roman"\;color:black\;mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>We <b>represent 
	employee shareholders as a whole</b>. We are regularly in contact with all
	 those who build tomorrow’s bank: (1) actors on the field who face clien
	ts every day and (2) collaborators in central services</span></span><span 
	lang=EN-US style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"\;mso-ansi-lang
	uage:EN-US'><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=xxxmsolistparagraph style='ms
	o-list:l1 level1 lfo7'><span class=xapple-converted-space><span lang=EN-US
	 style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"\;color:black\;mso-ansi-l
	anguage:EN-US'>We are <b>close to decision-making center and ambassadors o
	f all areas and jobs at the same time</b></span></span><span lang=EN-US st
	yle='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"\;mso-ansi-language:EN-US'><
	o:p></o:p></span></li></ul><p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='m
	so-fareast-font-family:Calibri\;mso-ansi-language:EN-US'><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p
	></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><b><u><span lang=EN-US style='color:red\
	;mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>To vote:<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p><p class=M
	soPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>You need your
	 access codes for <span class=SpellE>Esalia</span> and <span class=SpellE>
	Sharinbox</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-
	US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>ESALIA (8 or 9 digit login): <a href="h
	ttps://www.esalia.com/">https://www.esalia.com/</a><o:p></o:p></span></p><
	p class=MsoPlainText><span class=SpellE><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-l
	anguage:EN-US'>Sharinbox</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-lan
	guage:EN-US'> (8 digit login): <a href="https://sharinbox.societegenerale.
	com/">https://sharinbox.societegenerale.com/</a><o:p></o:p></span></p><p c
	lass=MsoNormal style='text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ans
	i-language:EN-US'>If you can’t find your ID\, launch: </span><a href="ht
	tps://socgen-portal.globalrelay.com/"><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-lan
	guage:EN-US'>https://socgen-portal.globalrelay.com/</span></a><span lang=E
	N-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNor
	mal style='text-autospace:none'><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:
	EN-US'>In the search bar : </span><a href="mailto:mailer@issuer.sgss.socie
	tegenerale.com"><span lang=EN-US style='color:windowtext\;mso-ansi-languag
	e:EN-US\;text-decoration:none\;text-underline:none'>mailer@issuer.sgss.soc
	ietegenerale.com</span></a><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US
	'><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='mso-
	ansi-language:EN-US'><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><b
	><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>VOTE for LEPAGNOL/LE VAI
	LLANT</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>\, of cou
	rse!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal style='text-autospace:none'><
	span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p></span><
	/p><p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'>
	Thank you for your support!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoPlainText><sp
	an lang=EN-US style='mso-ansi-language:EN-US'><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p></span></p
	><p class=MsoPlainText>Jérôme et Caroline<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoPlai
	nText><span class=SpellE><i>Let’s</i></span><i> <span class=SpellE>write
	</span> the future?<o:p></o:p></i></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style='mso-
	bidi-font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp\;</o:p></span></p></div></body></html>
